            <title>[CASSANDRA-5478] Nodetool clearsnapshot incorrectly reports to have requested a snapshot</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-5478</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When running &quot;nodetool clearsnapshot&quot; all existing snapshots are removed, but the following message is printed:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;./nodetool clearsnapshot&lt;br/&gt;
Requested snapshot for: all keyspaces &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Instead it should just print a single line stating that all snapshots have been removed.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>&lt;p&gt;MacOS, Datastax Cassandra 1.2.2&lt;/p&gt;</environment>
